PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Communiations of William D.S. Bowering, of Kelowna, British Columbia, as a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the National Museum of Science and Technology to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Norman Keevil, who has resigned.
